=head1 USE

If you use the C<contact_us> keyword, bigtop will create a CONTACT US POD
section in all of the controller modules.  This includes the base module
and its GEN piece, but not other GEN modules nor any models.

=head1 THE EXAMPLE

To see an example, build:

    bigtop -c example.bigtop all

Change to the Kids directory and look for C<example> in these files:

 docs/kids.bigtop
 lib/GENKids.pm
 lib/Kids.pm
 lib/Kids/Child.pm

